translate portuguese micha7_fb27d9a1:

    # pc "You don't have to be nervous around me. I'm not going to hurt you."
    pc "Não precisas de ficar nervosa comigo. Não te vou magoar."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:89
translate portuguese micha7_27577933:

    # mc "I know. I really want you to like me."
    mc "Eu sei. Quero mesmo que gostes de mim."

