    mc "Desculpa. Acho que ainda não estou pronta para isso."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:108
translate portuguese micha7_7d63d9da:

    # mc "I am very sorry. Did I offend you?"
    mc "Peço imensa desculpa. Ofendi-te?"

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:109
translate portuguese micha7_8b131ed8:

    # mc "I did not mean I would not want to go to bed with you. But I feel uncomfortable about it right now."
    mc "Não quis dizer que não quisesse ir para a cama contigo. Mas sinto-me desconfortável com isso neste momento."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:110
translate portuguese micha7_0d2c9d39:

    # pc "It's okay, I wasn't suggesting that. You didn't offend me."
    pc "Não faz mal, não estava a sugerir isso. Não me ofendeste."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:113
translate portuguese micha7_0e8b4e1b:

    # mc "Oh no, I am making things worse aren't I?"
    mc "Oh não, estou a piorar as coisas, não estou?"

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:114
translate portuguese micha7_c767c9ce:

    # mc "I am so bad at this."
    mc "Sou tão mau nisto."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:115
translate portuguese micha7_c1e312a1:

    # pc "It's okay, really. Just calm down."
    pc "Não faz mal, a sério. Acalma-te."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:118
translate portuguese micha7_87a0b25e:

    # "I reach over and place my hand over hers. She starts to pull away at first, then relaxes."
    "Estendo a mão e coloco-a sobre a dela. Ela começa por se afastar, mas depois relaxa."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:121
translate portuguese micha7_7c1c3cc4:

    # mc "Miss Spann did not tell me that you asked for this date. I thought that she set it up because she wanted me to meet people."
    mc "A Sra. Spann não me disse que foste tu que pediste este encontro. Pensei que ela o tivesse marcado porque queria que eu conhecesse pessoas."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:122
translate portuguese micha7_36fab42e:

    # mc "It does make me feel better that you requested it."
    mc "Faz-me sentir melhor saber que foste tu que pediste."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:123
translate portuguese micha7_f3c20824:

    # mc "Why did you want to buy me coffee?"
    mc "Porque é que quiseste pagar-me um café?"

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:124
translate portuguese micha7_f0ffbaf0:

    # pc "I don't know. I thought you were cute and could use a friend."
    pc "Não sei. Achei-te gira e pensei que precisavas de um amigo."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:127
translate portuguese micha7_41d2c325:

    # mc "You think that I am cute?"
    mc "Achas que sou gira?"

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:128
translate portuguese micha7_d54e19e4:

    # pc "Yeah. You're very cute."
    pc "Sim. És muito gira."

