    # pc "Can we at least try this again sometime?"
    pc "Podemos pelo menos tentar isto outra vez algum dia?"

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:168
translate portuguese micha7_d6451512:

    # "She makes a squeaking sound somewhere deep in her throat, as if the words are being forcefully pushed out."
    "Ela emite um som estridente no fundo da garganta, como se as palavras estivessem a ser forçadas a sair."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:169
translate portuguese micha7_f800bed0:

    # mc "Yes."
    mc "Sim."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:172
translate portuguese micha7_f5c4b536:

    # "Then she practically runs out of the café."
    "Depois, ela praticamente sai a correr do café."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:175
translate portuguese micha7_b95ac3d7:

    # "Well that was definitely one of the weirder first dates I've had. Not sure what was going on with her."
    "Bem, este foi definitivamente um dos primeiros encontros mais estranhos que já tive. Não sei bem o que se passava com ela."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:176
translate portuguese micha7_9788c24f:

    # "But she did say yes to another date."
    "Mas ela disse que sim a outro encontro."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:179
